<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,266,1396,1421]" pageId="1" pageNumber="295">Diagnosis</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Cao, H. Z. &amp; Chen, H. W." box="[284,502,1396,1421]" pageId="1" pageNumber="295" pagination="251 - 254" refId="ref4118" refString="Cao, H. Z. &amp; Chen, H. W. (2008) Discovery of the genus Luzonimyia Malloch in China, with descriptions of two new species (Insecta, Diptera, Drosophilidae). The Raffles Bulletin of Zoology, 56, 251 - 254." type="journal article" year="2008">Cao &amp; Chen 2008</bibRefCitation>
